OL,3,CTwo more arrested after teenager
OL,4,Cstabbed outside Smethwick mosque
OL,6,FTwo boys have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder in connection with
OL,8,Fthe death of another teenager outside
OL,9,Fa mosque in Smethwick last month.
OL,11,FIt's after 18-year-old Zeshan Afzal
OL,12,Fdied after being stabbed on Oldbury
OL,13,FRoad on the 20th of February.
OL,15,FTwo boys, aged 14 and 17, were
OL,16,Farrested following warrants carried
OL,17,Fout yesterday (4 April) and this
OL,18,Fmorning (5 April) in Smethwick.
OL,20,FBoth remain in custody whilst they are
OL,21,Fbeing questioned.
